      "title": "1590 dengue patients in a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Health, 1590 dengue cases have been reported in the past week.",
        "50.8 percent of those patients have been reported from the Western Province",
        "Meanwhile, the Dengue Control Unit said that 56 Health Medical Officer Divisions have been designated as Dengue High Risk Zones."
      ],
